PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,FThe 37-year-old, from Basingstoke,
OL,7,Fsuffered major injuries including a
OL,8,Fbroken neck and multiple fractures and
OL,9,Fsevere injuries to his eyes.
OL,11,FHe was told his eye would be lost due
OL,12,Fto the injuries.His eyelids were torn
OL,13,Faway, his iris ` the coloured part of
OL,14,Fthe eye ` has disappeared and he had a
OL,15,Fdetached retina ` the thin layer of
OL,16,Ftissue at the back of the eye which
OL,17,Fprocesses light and converts it into
OL,18,Fthe electrical signals that the brain
OL,19,Finterprets as images.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,FThere were large puncture wounds,
OL,7,Fleaving Mr Hurd with a gaping hole in
OL,8,Fhis right eye.Mr Hurd, who works in
OL,9,Fsales, was told that it was likely the
OL,10,Feye could not be repaired.
OL,12,FBut thanks to a series of intricate
OL,13,Fprocedures Mr Hurd's eye was rebuilt
OL,14,Fand while his good eye "does all the
OL,15,Fheavy lifting" he now can use the
OL,16,Finjured eye for depth and spatial
OL,17,Fawareness, enabling him to drive.
OL,26,@vD@XOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,FThe accident happened in 2023 while he
OL,7,Fwas on holiday with his fiancee Katie
OL,8,FPlimmer and friend, Gabby Thind.He was
OL,9,Fin the front passenger seat of a taxi
OL,10,Fwhich was T-boned by a drunk driver in
OL,11,Fa van who drove through a red light,
OL,12,Fsending the taxi into a spin which in
OL,13,Fturn knocked over a cyclist and a
OL,14,Fpedestrian.
OL,16,F"I can remember it like it was
OL,17,Fyesterday," he told the Press
OL,18,FAssociation.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,F"I had a broken neck with three large
OL,7,Ffractures going through the top of my
OL,8,Fspine towards the scull."One of the
OL,9,Ffractures could have been a complete
OL,10,Fgame-changer... I could have been
OL,11,Fparalysed.
OL,13,F"There was significant damage from the
OL,14,Fglass ` a shower of glass went
OL,15,Fstraight into the side of my face and
OL,16,Fa lot of pieces directly in my eye.
OL,18,F"The eye so was badly damaged."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@YOUuD@AOUzD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,FHis fiancee had bits of glass embedded
OL,7,Fin her skin which needed to be removed
OL,8,Fand their friend damaged the tendons
OL,9,Fin her hand.
OL,11,FMr Hurd passed out and was cut from
OL,12,Fthe car by emergency services before
OL,13,Fbeing rushed to hospital.
OL,15,FHe was put in an induced coma for a
OL,16,Fnumber of days and surgeons performed
OL,17,Fa procedure to save his eyelids and
OL,18,Fremove glass from the eye.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,FA second procedure was also performed
OL,7,Fbut was not a success and Mr Hurd was
OL,8,Ftold that it was likely he would lose
OL,9,Fhis eye.
OL,11,F"I woke up from my coma and there was
OL,12,Fa lady saying 'we have done the best
OL,13,Fthat we could but there is a high
OL,14,Fchance you are going to lose your eye'.
OL,16,F"So that was quite a shock, it was the
OL,17,Flast thing I expected to hear.
OL,19,F"It was quite an emotional time as you
OL,20,Fcan imagine."
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,FWhen he was well enough to come back
OL,7,Fto England, Mr Hurd went straight to
OL,8,Fthe hospital where he was referred
OL,9,Fprivately to Professor Roger Shimizu
OL,10,FWong, consultant ophthalmic surgeon at
OL,11,Fthe London Clinic.
OL,13,FAt this point his eye was "more like a
OL,14,Fraisin than an eyeball".
OL,26,@uD@[OUvD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,F"He got me into surgery pretty quickly
OL,7,Fand luckily it was a great success, he
OL,8,Fwas able to reattach the retina,
OL,9,Fremove the blood, and reattach the
OL,10,Fglobe ` the front part of the eye `
OL,11,Fand stabilise the puncture wounds," Mr
OL,12,FHurd said.
OL,14,F"That was just the very beginning of
OL,15,Fthe journey, unfortunately.
OL,17,F"I needed another surgery for the
OL,18,Fretina and then another to put in a
OL,19,Ffake iris ` a silicone iris that he
OL,20,Fwas able to put into the eye.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@cO]vD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,F"So I have fake colour in my eye. It
OL,7,Flooks really real but you can tell
OL,8,Fslight differences, it's a little bit
OL,9,Flighter than my actual eye."
OL,11,FMr Hurd then needed another procedure
OL,12,Fto replace a filter in the eye which
OL,13,Fcleans the eye."That was actually from
OL,14,Fa donor ` someone who had
OL,15,Funfortunately passed away," he added.
OL,17,F"It has just been a long, long healing
OL,18,Ftime, it has been a very long journey.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]uD@POUwD@[O]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,F"I can see shapes and colour and I
OL,7,Fhave peripheral vision. The good eye
OL,8,Fdoes all the heavy
OL,9,Flifting."Considering how badly damaged
OL,10,Fit was it is a miracle that I have
OL,11,Feven got that."
OL,13,FProfessor Wong said: "Whenever you
OL,14,Fhave a ruptured globe it is not good
OL,15,Fnews, the first thing I would tell the
OL,16,Fpatient is: 'there's a chance that you
OL,17,Fwill lose that eye'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IOUsD@OO]uD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,F"That's how bad it is."And so if we
OL,7,Fcome out of it, and he keeps the eye,
OL,8,Fthat's great, and down, further down
OL,9,Fthe line, you get some vision, that's
OL,10,Feven better."
OL,12,FHe said that Mr Hurd presented with no
OL,13,Fvision at all, and the first operation
OL,14,Fhelped to "tidy things up".
OL,16,F"The globe was still leaking," he
OL,17,Fsaid."It was actually a bit more like
OL,18,Fa raisin, rather than an eyeball, than
OL,19,Fa globe.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@WOUrD@MO]vD@KOUvD@ZO]xD@AOUxD@
OL,26,A^O]yD@FOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,F"So that was repaired."Professor Wong,
OL,7,Fwho specialises in vitreo retinal
OL,8,Fdiseases and ocular trauma as well as
OL,9,Fother eye conditions such as macular
OL,10,Fdiseases and complicated cataract
OL,11,Fsurgery, went on: "That was the first
OL,12,Fstep, which is basically making a
OL,13,Fglobe a globe... to repair the
OL,14,Frupture, let the eye settle.
OL,16,F"And then we planned to do a series
OL,17,Foperations."You kind of need to do it
OL,18,Fone step at a time."Initial work was
OL,19,Fdone to "keep the globe intact,
OL,20,Fpressure normal and the retina in
OL,21,Fplace", he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@WO]sD@SOUxD@AOUyD@LOUzD@TO]{D@
OL,26,AIOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777626370
OL,3,CMan's eye rebuilt after eight
OL,4,Coperations following car crash
OL,6,F"Once that was achieved, then we start
OL,7,Fto look at the icing on the
OL,8,Fcake."Before that, I was just trying
OL,9,Fto see if there was a cake."
OL,11,FHe added: "I've known Chris for a
OL,12,Flittle while now, I've seen him quite
OL,13,Fa few times and to see him change from
OL,14,Fwhen we first met, and then through
OL,15,Fthe multiple operations and seeing
OL,16,Fwhere he is now, and what he's able to
OL,17,Fdo, is fulfilling.
OL,19,F"It's great to see people be able to
OL,20,Fget back to a normal-ish lifestyle."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@FOUqD@\O]sD@KOU{D@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
